The '''''Blue Fox''''' was an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] under the service to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. She launched an unsuccessful attempt to destroy the [[MC80 Star Cruiser/Legends|MC80 Star Cruiser]] ''[[Excelsior]]'' that was trying to enter [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]]. Blue Fox was destroyed by [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|T-65 X-wing starfighters]] and [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|BTL Y-wing starfighters]] sent by the Excelsior.

